      "comment": "LEKTRA SKIP (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (30.77) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Ready to return to form. OLLIE LIMES (1) found the going tougher but ran well to place over 512m at this track (30.18) in Grade 6. Was a winner the start prior in easier at this track. Expected to feature again. MOONLIGHT RIVER (4) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at Horsham over 485m behind Naradhan (28.02) in a Grade 4/5. The form out of last race has been strong. Worth following up. DURAN NIRVANA (8) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
